      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3a · DUMP INICIAL (por collection, paralelo)\n\ncursor find().sort({_id:-1})  →  lotes de 500\npor doc (olha o destino):\n   ausente → insert · hash igual → skip\n   hash difere → update · hot → skip\na cada lote: grava dumpCursorId (fronteira)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 13,
      "containerId": "el15",
      "originalText": "3a · DUMP INICIAL (por collection, paralelo)\n\ncursor find().sort({_id:-1})  →  lotes de 500\npor doc (olha o destino):\n   ausente → insert · hash igual → skip\n   hash difere → update · hot → skip\na cada lote: grava dumpCursorId (fronteira)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    },
